    "created_at": "2015-11-26T01:51:11Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-26T01:51:11Z",
    "body": "You can create the window with `show` set to false and then listen to the `dom-ready` and `did-fail-load` events.\nIf you get the `did-fail-load` with a matching url, the server is not available and you should show the error message. If you get `dom-ready` the server is available and you should show the page. Details are in the webContens and BrowserWindow docs.\n"
  },
