    "created_at": "2015-12-06T18:52:27Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-06T18:52:27Z",
    "body": "Don't loop. Just use a tries counter. Each time you try to load again, inc the tries. When tries get to your max tries and you get \"did-fail-load\", exit (show the error message only once you reach max tries).\n"
